{"tid":2361942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向太歌頌台灣政府「英明神武」 為求團聚與老公補辦台北結婚","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:31:11.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb699da7b35fb9b370f7a29391cc3f2c0f0069ae","tid":2361942,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210110/O5W3CDR2PJHQ7FUH2YTJAM23SY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210110%2FO5W3CDR2PJHQ7FUH2YTJAM23SY%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=aa75b3b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210110%2FO5W3CDR2PJHQ7FUH2YTJAM23SY%2F&h=6fb8b3f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210110/O5W3CDR2PJHQ7FUH2YTJAM23SY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敢言的向華強太太陳嵐，一直愛國，近來弄孫為樂的她，少有出政治相關的post，反而是孫女至上，向太昨日為孫女「小奶皇」設百日宴慶祝，今日她在微博貼圖開心share，字裏行間除了講湊孫，更用了較多的篇幅不停歌頌台灣政府的好之外，更自爆老公及兒子都向佐齊齊做了台灣女婿，覺得為他們申請「依親居留」，絕對合情理。"},{"pid":"74812734dffbd148c3acc0f4205cf93a5e043c2d","tid":2361942,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc7e0557a34985f1a60d1b40ef08a62fa874326","tid":2361942,"uid":301820,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"反台是工作<br />\n移台是生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f9a4f8a6600cfed5bc4813a248116bad7def85","tid":2361942,"uid":13745,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"大家應該要留意下<br />\n點解姓向既回歸後親中點解突然間變親台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f420dcfec8771ab97fd34ed21c76a8e5a4adb9","tid":2361942,"uid":71596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:11:51.000Z